name: GDG DevFest 2015 - October 11, 2015

### Join us at GDG DevFest

Watch this space for more information about our family-friendly hackathon hosted by the Google Developer Groups in Colorado!

### Sponsors

We have some great sponsors - more info coming soon!

### Location

Google Boulder, 2590 Pearl St #110, Boulder, CO 80302 

### Hosts

* GDG Boulder - [meetup](http://www.meetup.com/Google-Developer-Group-Boulder/)
* GDG Denver - [meetup](http://www.meetup.com/GDG-Denver/)
* GDG Northern Colorado [meetup](http://www.meetup.com/GDGNoCo/) [google developers](https://developers.google.com/groups/chapter/100148220005153084415/)
